    "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 4.0",
    "body" : "<p>There is an option (checkbox) to permanently change all primitives to display as <strong>Hex</strong> under the options for Data Views.  See:</p>\n\n<p><strong>Settings</strong> > <strong>Build, Execution, Deployment</strong> > <strong>Debugger</strong> > <strong>Data Views</strong> > <strong>Java</strong> > </p>\n\n<p><code>\"Show hex value for primitives\"</code></p>\n\n<p><a href=\"https://i.sstatic.net/5vk4m.png\" rel=\"nofollow noreferrer\"><img src=\"https://i.sstatic.net/5vk4m.png\" alt=\"enter image description here\"></a></p>\n"
  }, {
    "comments" : [ {
      "owner" : {
