      "content_license" : "CC BY-SA 3.0",
      "body" : "Using the Java Data Type Renderers for primitive types, I was able to use this expression to view both decimal and hexidecimal values for all ints: this + &quot; [&quot; + String.format(&quot;0x%08x&quot;, this) + &quot;]&quot;"
    } ],
